    "strings": [
      "CONFIDENTIAL",
      "Capitol Insurance Advisors",
      "Marcus Jennings, Senior Vice President",
      "03/15/2026",
      "RE: Hill Country Hospitality Partners, LLC \u2014 Transfer Submission",
      "401 Congress Avenue, Suite 2800, Austin, TX, 78701",
      "To: Underwriting Department, Hallmark Insurance Group",
      "Dear Underwriting Team,",
      "Account Overview",
      "We are pleased to submit ",
      "Hill Country Hospitality Partners, LLC",
      " for your review and consideration. The insured is a",
      "boutique hotel ownership and management with integrated restaurant and event operations across Central and South Texas,",
      "headquartered in Austin, with approximately 16 years of operating history. Coverage is requested for Workers' Compensation,",
      "General Liability, Commercial Property.",
      "Coverage Requested",
      "Workers' Compensation:",
      " Workers' Compensation coverage is requested for approximately 285 employees across all",
      "operations.",
      "General Liability:",
      " Commercial General Liability with occurrence limits of $1,000,000.00 per occurrence and $2,000,000.00",
      "general aggregate.",
      "Commercial Property:",
      " Commercial Property coverage for all scheduled locations on a special form with replacement cost",
      "valuation.",
      "Loss History Summary",
      "The claims history warrants review; management has implemented corrective measures to address identified exposures. Over",
      "the review period, the insured has incurred ",
      "38",
      " total claims with ",
      "$511,891.20",
      " in total paid losses and ",
      "$714,517.96",
      " total",
      "incurred. Currently, ",
      "11",
      " claims remain open and ",
      "27",
      " have been closed.",
      "Annualized loss ratio is ",
      "21.6%",
      " (avg annual incurred $142,903.59 against current annual premium $660,422.75 over 5 loss",
      "years).",
      "Breakdown by coverage line:",
      "\u2022 ",
      " 28 claims, $324,545.30 paid, $415,934.50 incurred",
      " 8 claims, $8,779.76 paid, $82,656.15 incurred",
      " 2 claims, $178,566.14 paid, $215,927.31 incurred",
      "Note: account experienced a cancellation in ",
      "2022-2023",
      " with Zurich Insurance Group. Reason: Insured cancelled \u2014 moved to",
      "current carrier.",
      "Risk Highlights",
      "\u2022 The insured carries contractual risk transfer provisions in all subcontractor and vendor agreements.",
      "\u2022 An employee assistance program and workplace wellness initiative have been in place for over five years.",
      "\u2022 A comprehensive fleet management program with GPS tracking and driver training has been in place since 2023.",
      "\u2022 The insured maintains a dedicated safety committee that meets monthly and conducts quarterly site audits.",
      "\u2022 The insured has implemented a formal return-to-work program that has reduced lost-time claims by over 30%.",
      "\u2022 Favorable experience modification factor of 0.94, reflecting a strong loss control program relative to class peers.",
      "\u2022 With 285 employees and a structured HR program, the insured maintains low turnover and consistent safety training.",
      "Broker Recommendation",
      "We believe this account represents a well-managed risk and look forward to establishing a strong partnership.",
      "Please do not hesitate to contact us with any questions or if additional information is required.",
      "Respectfully submitted,",
      "Marcus Jennings",
      "Senior Vice President",
      "Page 1 of 2",
      "Page 2 of 2"
    ],
